    <content>&lt;P&gt;While executing the FM&amp;nbsp;FAGL_GET_GL_DOCUMENT, I am getting the below dump.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Ankita05_0-1725538896216.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/162932iAA3190E5BBF0DFFB/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Ankita05_0-1725538896216.png" alt="Ankita05_0-1725538896216.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I have analyzed and found that The error is coming from below class CL_ABAP_CORRESPONDING-&amp;gt; EXECUTE. Inside this I do not find any executable statement here to debug this.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;How to debug and find the root cause of the variable which is giving overflow error.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Ankita05_1-1725539012185.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/162933i8AA002A715B42531/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Ankita05_1-1725539012185.png" alt="Ankita05_1-1725539012185.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;According to me , It is coming from the below variable MSL&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Ankita05_2-1725539163397.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/162934i03383AC58FD5D137/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Ankita05_2-1725539163397.png" alt="Ankita05_2-1725539163397.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Could you please check it.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/getting-dump-in-fm-fagl-get-gl-document/qaq-p/13855759"/>
